知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8962b7f8d79ce365acedc7d6922f9b469645122e","tid":1533437,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e254cd60d1a829792afb01bdb6480bb7a9fde3c5","tid":1533437,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c184053eb0c04da7f0dd2c158f7d9fda64960833","tid":1533437,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72807c56c019fe46c50b8a8de5b77e145ccafd35","tid":1533437,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3ac27afdbfbbd94381cb30e5969193335393396","tid":1533437,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"回歸初心，推"},{"pid":"746f1dc7a15f1273039d1c10cc98b6186b3d3d54","tid":1533437,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crzdsEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrzdsEZ.jpg&h=1c47cc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[禍必及妻兒]所有人FB/IG等等即刻轉頭像<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"743a814291d7dd5ee1856caaf0c1bdadbe9b59c4","tid":1533437,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd13acc83e4c8daf6d4339f222dbdec01710fca5","tid":1533437,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"ご署名をお願いします！<br />\n香港における政府当局による強権的な動きをけん制するため、日本版『香港人権・民主主義法案』の議論を開始することを日本の国会議員に求めます。<br />\nPlease submit your signature!<br />\nWe are asking Japanese parliamentarians to start discussions on the Japanese version of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FrqWFBmbSp4&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgbrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=26fe3275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4</a> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手簽同share. Thank you."},{"pid":"487bf0383e2a458653ec3b3124daa9795b513b0b","tid":1533437,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}